                </div>

                <div class="row mt-5 mx-5">
                    <div class="col-md-12 alert bg-color-list" role="alert">
                        <ul class="font-if">
                            <li>
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success me-3"></i>IGSTC supports participants with an active role in the workshop. Participant should be
                                a speaker in the workshop.</li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success me-3"></i>PAN-India/Germany presence of participants is necessary.</li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success me-3"></i>The overall number of invited participants should be 30 (appx.). Students and young researchers
                                from the hosting institution may attend the
                                <br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; workshop programme.</li>
                            <li>
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success me-3"></i>Click on Save as Draft to regularly save the data.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-3 mx-5">
                    <!-- <div class="col-md-1"></div> -->
                    <!-- <div class="col-md-12 alert" role="alert">
                                <ul>
                                    <li><h4 class="pb-3 color-theme"><b>
